PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779494576
OL,3,CUK scientists developing Ebola vaccine
OL,4,Cas outbreak spreads 'rapidly' in Congo
OL,6,FThe rare strain of Ebola currently
OL,7,Fspreading in the Democratic Republic
OL,8,Fof the Congo, known as Bundibugyo, has
OL,9,Fno proven vaccine and kills between
OL,10,F30% and 50% of those it infects.
OL,12,FThis has prompted WHO Director-
OL,13,FGeneral, Tedros Adhanom Ghebreyesus,
OL,14,Fto raise the agency's risk assessment
OL,15,Ffor Congo to "very high," up from its
OL,16,Fprevious rating of high.
OL,18,FThe risk remains high for regional
OL,19,Fspread and low at global levels, he
OL,20,Ftold reporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779494576
OL,3,CUK scientists developing Ebola vaccine
OL,4,Cas outbreak spreads 'rapidly' in Congo
OL,6,FProfessor Teresa Lambe, Calleva head
OL,7,Fof vaccine immunology at the OVG,
OL,8,Fsaid: "My hope is that this outbreak
OL,9,Fcan be brought under control quickly
OL,10,Fand that vaccines are ultimately not
OL,11,Fneeded.
OL,13,F"Nevertheless, our team and partners
OL,14,Fwill continue working to ensure that
OL,15,Fpotential vaccine options are
OL,16,Favailable if they are needed.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779494576
OL,3,CUK scientists developing Ebola vaccine
OL,4,Cas outbreak spreads 'rapidly' in Congo
OL,6,F"The ability to move rapidly in
OL,7,Fsituations like this has been built on
OL,8,Fmany years of vaccine research and
OL,9,Fclose collaboration with our global
OL,10,Fpartners."
OL,12,FThe OVG previously tested Ebola
OL,13,Fvaccines in response to the 2013-2016
OL,14,FWest Africa outbreak, which
OL,15,Fcontributed to a different Ebola
OL,16,Fvaccine being approved by the European
OL,17,FMedicines Agency in 2020.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
