OL,3,CUK scientists developing Ebola vaccine
OL,4,Cas outbreak spreads 'rapidly' in Congo
OL,6,FEarlier on Friday, the United Nations
OL,7,Fsaid it released $60 million (about
OL,8,F#45 million) from its Central
OL,9,FEmergency Response Fund to accelerate
OL,10,Fthe response in Congo and in the
OL,11,Fregion.
OL,13,FThe US and UK have pledged millions in
OL,14,Ffunding to bolster the response in
OL,15,FCongo and Uganda.
OL,17,FAnnouncing the funding last week,
OL,18,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,19,F"It is vital we act now to save lives
OL,20,F` outbreaks like Ebola do not stop at
OL,21,Fborders, and neither can we."
OL,26,@{D@AOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
