OL,3,CUK scientists developing Ebola vaccine
OL,4,Cas outbreak spreads 'rapidly' in Congo
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FOn Thursday, residents in Rwampara
OL,12,Fburned an Ebola treatment centre in
OL,13,Feastern Congo after people were
OL,14,Fstopped from retrieving the body of a
OL,15,Flocal man.
OL,17,FThe bodies of those who die from Ebola
OL,18,Fcan be highly contagious and lead to
OL,19,Ffurther spread when people prepare
OL,20,Fbodies for burial and gather for
OL,21,Ffunerals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
