PN,31409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1779494576
OL,3,CUK scientists developing Ebola vaccine
OL,4,Cas outbreak spreads 'rapidly' in Congo
OL,6,FThis is Congo's 17th Ebola outbreak,
OL,7,Fand the WHO has said the country's
OL,8,Fhealth ministry has experienced staff
OL,9,Fand capacity to respond. Most
OL,10,Foutbreaks, however, were of the more
OL,11,Fcommon Ebola type.
OL,13,FOutbreaks of the disease occur
OL,14,Fperiodically in Africa, with the most
OL,15,Fsevere taking place in West Africa
OL,16,Fbetween 2014 and 2016 and leading to
OL,17,Fmore than 11,000 deaths.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
